note=Knuth SGB save_graph opened with fopen(f,"w") so Windows text mode wrote CRLF for internal newlines; a graph saved on Windows could not restore on Linux. Erratum page 414 (Dec 2025) changes to "wb". Mirror ascherer/sgb c0943fd (2025-09-29) to 88fac2f (2025-12-28). Trusted driver simulates TEXTMODE_CRLF on the buggy rev so the Linux runner catches it.
